name: Synth sETH
description: Synth sETH is an experimental blockchain token created for academic and research purposes in DeFi. It is independent from the original sETH and not for public investment.
extended_description: This token is designed for research on DeFi user behavior and network interactions. The original sETH is undergoing migration with reduced trading activity, which allows this token to be used for testing and academic studies. More details are on our website and social media.
